quran[128]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Wẽnd yellã waame, bɩ y ra yãg ne-a ye, A yɩlgame n zẽk n yi bãmb sẽn maand-A lagem-n-taarã ne wã."
  16,2,"A sikda malεgsã ne wahɩ wã sẽn yɑɑ A sagellã, A sẽn tʋll ɑ soɑb nengẽ A yembsã pʋgẽ, tɩ b bugs n yeel tɩ: ""soab ka be rẽnda Maam, bɩ y zoe-Ma""."
  16,3,"A naana saasã la tẽngã ne sɩda, A Naam yɩ wagell n yi b sẽn maand-A lagem-n-taar ne wã."
  16,4,"A naana ninsaala sẽn tũ ne mani, t'a yik n yɑɑ no-koeem zɑɑl soab vẽeneg-vẽenega."
  16,5,"La rũmsã, A naan-b lame n kõ yãmba. Bee b pʋgẽ, yãmb sẽn yiisd wɑood teed b pʋgẽ, la yõod a taab me. Bee b pʋgẽ me yãmb sẽn rɩte."
  16,6,"Lɑ b tɑrɑ rɑsãnd yãmb gesgẽ y sã n wa n kẽesd-b zɑɑbre la y sẽn wɑt n pɑkd-b yibeoog n nɑ n rɑɑge."
  16,7,"La b zɩlgd yãmb zɩɩbã n kẽngd tẽng ning yãmb sẽn da pa tõe n ta rẽndame tɩ tũu ne yaamse, ad yãmb Soabã yaa nin-bãan-zoεt n yaa yolsg naaba."
  16,8,"La wiidi wã ne bõensã, yɑɑ y nɑ zombdẽ n le yaa faas teedo. La A naand yãmb sẽn pa mi."
  16,9,"Ad so-tɩrgã wĩnigr bee ne Wẽnde, bala soe sãnda yaa golemse. A sã n rata A kãndgada-y fãa gilli."
  16,10,"Yẽnd n sikd koom saasẽ wã yãmb yũub yĩnga, la tɩɩs me yiisg tɩ y wãbendẽ."
  16,11,"A bulsda ne-ɑ koodã lɑ zaetʋʋnã la tɑmar tɩɩsã la sib-rãmbã lɑ tɩ-biisã buud fãɑ, ad bee rẽ pʋgẽ tagmas ne neb sẽn tagsde."
  16,12,"La A wõr n kõ yãmba, yʋngã la wĩndgã. Wĩntoogã la kiuugã la ãdsã yaa sẽn wõr ne A saglga, ad tagmas bee woto pʋgẽ ne neb sẽn ya yam-rãmba."
  16,13,"Lɑ A sẽn naan n kõ yãmb tẽngã zugã, sẽn yɑɑ kõbg toor-toore, ad tɑgmɑs be woto pʋgẽ ne neb sẽn tɑgsd n getẽ."
  16,14,"La leb n yaa Yẽ n nom mogrã n kõ yãmba, sẽn na yɩl tɩ y rɩ nemd sẽn yɑɑ mɑɑs ɑ pʋgẽ, la y yiisd ɑ pʋgẽ faas teed n yeelgdẽ, lɑ fo yãtɑ kogendã tɩ b pãrgd mogrã n rukdẽ, lɑ sẽn na le yɩl tɩ y bao A yɩɩdlemã, tɩ sãnd-sãnd me y na pʋʋs barka."
  16,15,"La A sela tẽn-gãngã zug tãmse, sẽn na yɩl t'a ra miim ne-y ye, la kʋɩls la soay sẽn na yɩl tɩ y tũudẽ."
  16,16,"La A mɑɑn tɑgmas-rãmbɑ, la ãdsã tɩ bãmb bãngd soay ne rẽ."
  16,17,"Rẽ yĩnga, ning sẽn naandã wã wõnda wala ned ning sẽn pa naandã wã, yãmb pa tɑgsd n gεtẽ lɑɑ?"
  16,18,"Lɑ ɑd yãmb sã n na n sõd Wẽnd neemã wã, y kõn n tõog n bãng b sõor ye, ad Wẽnd yaa yaafg naab n yaa yolsg naaba."
  16,19,"La Wẽnd mii bũmb ning y sẽn solgdã la y sẽn vẽnegdã."
  16,20,"La bõn-yood nins b sẽn boond zẽng sẽn pa Wẽndã, b pɑ tõe n naan baa fʋɩ, bãmb me b naan-b lame."
  16,21,"(B) Yaa kɩɩms n pɑ vʋɩɩs ye, b leb n pa mi wakat ning b sẽn na n yik-b kũumã poorẽ wã ye."
  16,22,"Yãmb Soabã yaa Soɑb yεnga, lɑ neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne yɑoolem rɑɑrã, b sũyã kɩɩsda rẽ tɩ b yaa waoog-m-mens rãmba."
  16,23,"Sik ka be tɩ Wẽnd mii b sẽn solgdã lɑ b sẽn vẽnegdã, ɑd A pa nong waoog-m-mens rãmb ye."
  16,24,"Lɑ b sã n yeel bãmba: ""yaa bõe la y Soabã siki? La b sẽn yete: "" yɑɑ pĩnd rãmb soɑlma!"
  16,25,"Tɩ b nɑ n wɑ tʋk b zɩɩbã poɑem dũni-yikrã raare, la neb nins bãmb sẽn menemsd tɩ pɑ tũ ne bãngrã me zɩɩbo. Ad bãmbã sẽn tʋkdã yɩ wẽnga."
  16,26,"Ad neb nins sẽn reng bãmb taoorã rag n maana raba, tɩ Wẽnd ta b meoongã yẽgrẽ n kɩt tɩ b meoongã gẽk n lʋɩ b zugu, tɩ sɩbgrã wɑ-b zĩig ning b sẽn n ka tẽedẽ."
  16,27,"Rẽ poorẽ, Dũni-yikr raarã A na n yãng-b lame la A yeel-bɑ:"" Mam lagem-n-taas nins yãmb sẽn da yɩ n zabd b yĩngã bεε?"" Tɩ bãngdbã yeele: "" ad yãnd la wẽng be kɩfr-rãmbã zug rũndã daarã."
  16,28,"Neb nins malεgsã sẽn reegd b yõyã tɩ b yaa wẽg-m-mens rãmbã, tɩ b na n sɑk n tũ nɑnɑ la b yeele: ""tõnd ra pa tʋmd wẽng buud ye!"" "" n-ye, ad Wẽnd mii yãmb sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  16,29,"Bɩ y kẽ gεhannem rɑgnoy wã, tɩ y yaa paadb ɑ pʋgẽ, rẽnd waoog-m-mens rãmbã gãɑg zĩig yɩ wẽnga!"
  16,30,"Tɩ b yeel neb nins sẽn zoe-b Wẽndã: ""yaa bõe la y Soabã siki?"" tɩ b na n yeele: "" yaa sõma"". Neb nins sẽn maan sõma dũni kaanẽ wã b tara rolb sẽn yaa sõma dũni; la yɑoolem rɑɑr zɑkã n yɩɩd sõmblem, lɑ ad wẽn-zoεtbã zɑk be neere!"
  16,31,"Arzãn zĩndidgã, la b na n kẽ, tɩ kʋɩlsã zoet b tẽngrã, b tɑrɑ b sẽn rat fãɑ a pʋgẽ, yaa woto la Wẽnd rond wẽn-zoεtbã."
  16,32,"Neb nins malεgsã sẽn reegd b yõyã tɩ b yaa nin-sõmã wã b yet-b lɑme: ""tɩlgr be y yĩnga! Kẽ-y arzãnã y sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã yĩngɑ""."
  16,33,"Rẽ yĩnga b gũuda bũmb n zʋʋg malεgsã wa wa bãmb nengẽ maa fo Soabã sagellã wa wa bãmba? Ad yaa woto la neb nins sẽn reng bãmbã maane, lɑ Wẽnd pa wẽdg ye, ad yaa bãmb n yɩ n wẽgd b mense."
  16,34,"Tɩ tʋʋm-beed nins bãmb sẽn maanã paam bãmba, tɩ b sẽn rag n yaand bũmb ningã wã gũbg-b n gilgi."
  16,35,"Tɩ neb nins sẽn maan lagem-n-taar ne Wẽndã yeele:"" Wẽnd sã n da tʋllẽ tõnd ra ka na n tũ baa fʋɩ zẽng sẽn pa Yẽ ye; tõndo lɑ d ba-rãmbã me ra pa na n maanẽ woto ye, d ra ka na hɑrem bũmb me ye"". Yaa woto lɑ neb nins sẽn reng bãmb tɑoorã maane, lɑ rẽ yĩngɑ bũmb roga Tẽn-tʋmdbã sã n ka taasg sẽn vẽnegde?"
  16,36,"Lɑ sɩdɑ, Tõnd tʋmsame tɩ kẽng zãma fãa nengẽ Tẽn-tʋʋma [sẽn na yɩl n t'a yeel-ba]: ""tũ-y Wẽnd la y zãag rʋbse, Tɩ be b pʋgẽ Wẽnd sẽn kãnde, la be b pʋgẽ meneng sẽn sɩdg b rãmb zugu. Bɩ y kẽn tẽngã zug n ges yagsdbã baasg yɩɩ wãn-wãnɑ?"
  16,37,"Baa tɩ fo sã n maand yã-beed ne b kãndagrã, ad Wẽnd pa kãndagd ned A sẽn menems ye, b pa tar sõangd buud me."
  16,38,"La b wẽen ne Wẽnd b pãng tεka: tɩ Wẽnd pa vʋʋgd ned sẽn ki ye. Ad pa sɩd ye! Ad yaa pʋleng sẽn yɑɑ sɩdɑ n rog A zugu, la ɑd nebã wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  16,39,"(A na n vʋʋg-b lame) sẽn na yɩl n vẽneg n wĩnig-ba b sẽn da yɩ n yõsd taab bũmb ning zugã, tɩ kɩfr-rãmbã me bãng tɩ bãmb rɑ yɩɩ zĩri-be-rãmba."
  16,40,"Ad Tõnd sã n rɑt yell t'ɑ yɩ, yɑɑ D yεεl-ɑ bal t'ɑ ""yɩ"" t'a be yɩɩbẽ."
  16,41,"La neb nins sẽn yik ne b dĩinã Wẽnd yĩnga, b sẽn wẽg-ba loogr poorẽ, D na zĩndg-b zĩig sẽn be neer dũni kaanẽ. La yɑoolem-raar keoorã n yɩɩd bedrem, tɩ b sã n da miime."
  16,42,"Neb nins sẽn maan-b sugr la b rɩk b mens n bobl ne b Soabã."
  16,43,"Lɑ Tõnd pa tʋms taoor tɩ fo pɑ wɑ rẽnda raopa; tɩ Tõnd tʋmd wahɩ wã b nengẽ. Bɩ y sok gɑfã rãmbã tɩ y sã n pa miẽ."
  16,44,"(Tõnd tʋms-b lame) ne vẽenem la gãf-rãmbã, La D sik Alkʋrãanã fo nengẽ sẽn na yɩl tɩ fo vẽneg n wĩnig nebã b sẽn sik n kõ-bã, lɑ sẽn nɑ yɩl tɩ b tagse."
  16,45,"Rẽ yĩngã sẽn rabsd-b wẽnsã maana bas-m-yam tɩ tẽngã kõn n bõr-bɑ? Maa sɩbgr wɑ b nengẽ b sẽn pa tẽed zĩĩg ningẽ?"
  16,46,"Maa a yõk-b b gilmã pʋsẽ tɩ b pa tõe n põs ye."
  16,47,"Maa a yõk-b b rɑbeemã pʋgẽ. Ad yãmb Soabã yaa nin-bãan-zoεt n yɑɑ yoalsdɑ."
  16,48,"Rẽ yĩnga b pa yãnd tɩ bũmb fãa Wẽnd sẽn nɑɑnã maasem yɑɑ sẽn kɩlld goɑbg lɑ rɩdgo, n maand suguud ne Wẽnde, tɩ b yɑɑ sẽn sik b mense?"
  16,49,"Lɑ yaa Wẽnd la sẽn be saasẽ la sẽn be tẽngẽ, sẽn yɑɑ bõn-yãnemds fãɑ maand suguudu, la malεgsã me, tɩ pa naag ne waoog-m-meng ye."
  16,50,"B yaeesda b Soabã sẽn be b yĩngrã, la b maand b sẽn sagl-b ne wã."
  16,51,"Lɑ Wẽnd yeelame: ""ra rɩk-y soab rãmb a yiib ye, ad Soab sẽn tũud yaa a yembr bala, bɩ y yaees Maam bɑlɑ""."
  16,52,"Lɑ Yẽ n so sẽn be saasẽ la tẽngẽ, lɑ yaa Yẽ n so tũudmã tɩ tɑb ne-A, rẽ yĩnga zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnd lɑ yãmb yaeesda?"
  16,53,"Lɑ neema fãa yãmb sẽn tare, yii Wẽnd nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ wẽng sã n paam yãmba, yaa Yẽ nengẽ lɑ yãmb lebdɑ."
  16,54,"Rẽ poorẽ, A sã n zẽk nɑngã n bas yãmba, la yãmb kẽer sẽn mɑɑn lɑg-m-tɑɑr ne b Soabã."
  16,55,"N na n kɩfl ne A sẽn kõ-b bũmb ningã wã, bɩ y wʋm noogo tɩ y na wɑ n bãnge!"
  16,56,"La b yãkd pʋɩɩr Tõnd sẽn rɩlg-b bũmb ningã pʋgẽ n kõt (b rʋbsã) b sẽn pa mi b rãmb yõodo. Ne Wẽnde! B na sok yãmb y sẽn da yɩ n naɑndẽ wã."
  16,57,"La b yet tɩ kom-pugli wã yɑɑ Wẽnd rẽndɑ; A naam yɩlgame! N yaool n kõt b mens bãmb sẽn nongã (kom-ribli)."
  16,58,"La b sã n noog b yembr fãɑ sũur ne bi-puglɑ la a nengã sẽn kelled n sobg t'ɑ yɑɑ sũ-toog soɑbɑ."
  16,59,"N solgd ɑ nebã b sẽn kõ-a kɩbɑr ne bũmb ningã wẽng yĩnga. A na n zã-a-la ne yɑɑlg bɩ ɑ na n bus-a-lɑ tomẽ? Ad bãmbã sẽn bʋʋdã yɩ wẽnga."
  16,60,"Neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne yaoolem rɑɑrã, bãmb n tar bilg wẽngã (b sẽn da yɩ n bilgd Wẽndã). La Wẽnd [A ye] n tɑr bilgr sẽn yɩɩd zẽkre, Yẽ me la a Winda, n yaa a Bʋʋd-mita."
  16,61,"La tɩ Wẽnd sã n da yõkda nebã ne b wẽgdã, A rag n ka na n bas tẽngã zug bõn-vũnung buud ye, la ad A yaoond-b lame n na n tãag wakat sẽn yãke, la b raarã sã n ta, b pa na n yaoolg-b ye, b leb n pa na n yãg ne-b ye."
  16,62,"La b kõt Wẽnd bãmb sẽn kis bũmb ningã, tɩ b zɩlmã yet zĩri tɩ bãmb tarɑ sẽn be neer Wẽnd nengẽ. Sik kae tɩ Bugum la b tɑrɑ, n na kẽ ne yãbgo."
  16,63,"Ne Wẽnde! Ad Tõnd ra tʋmɑme tɩ kẽng zãma fo taoore t'a Sʋtãan faas b tʋʋmã n kõ-bɑ, rẽnd yẽ lɑ b lall-n-taag rũndã, la b le tar sɩbgr sẽn zɑbde."
  16,64,"La Tõnd pa sik Gafã n kõ foom, rẽndame tɩ yaa sẽn na kɩt tɩ f vẽneg n kõ-ba b sẽn yõs taab bũmb ning zugã, n leb n yaa kãndagre, la yolsg n kõ neb nins sẽn kõt sɩdã."
  16,65,"La yaa Wẽnd n sik koom sẽn yit saasẽ, n vɩɩmsd tẽngã ne-a a sẽn ki poorẽ, ad bee rẽ pʋgẽ tagmas sɩd-sɩd ne neb sẽn wʋmde."
  16,66,"Ad bee rũmsã pʋgẽ, tags-n-gεsg n kõ yãmba: Tõnd yũnugda yãmb bũmb ning sẽn be rũmsã pʋsẽ wã, sẽn yit bĩnd la zɩɩm sʋka, tɩ yaa bĩisim n yɑɑ yɩlenga, n sɑkd loogr ne yũudba."
  16,67,"La tɩ-biisẽ wã, sẽn yi tamar tɩɩs la sibi, tɩ y yiisd bõn-yũudɩ sẽn suud la rɩtl sẽn yaa yɩlemde, ad bee woto pʋgẽ tagmas-rãmb n kõ neb sẽn tar yɑm."
  16,68,"La fo Soabã tʋmame tɩ kẽng sĩ wã nengẽ:"" rɩk-y tãensã n mɑɑn y roto, la tɩɩsã, la b sẽn yɑgendã."
  16,69,"Rẽ poorẽ rɩ-y tɩ-biis buud fãa la y rɩk y Soabã soyã sẽn kõogã. Tɩ bõn-yũudɩ yit b pʋsẽ wã kõbg sẽn yõs tɑɑbɑ, tɩ yaa tɩp-tɩɩm n kõ nebã be a pʋgẽ, ad tagmas be rẽ pugẽ ne neb sẽn tagsd n getẽ."
  16,70,"Ad yaa Wẽnd n naan yãmba; rẽ poorẽ t'A kʋ yãmba. Be yãmb sʋka b sẽn na n bas t'a kʋʋl n tɑ vɩɩm vũnug zĩigẽ, sẽn na yɩl t'a ra bãng baa fʋɩ ɑ sẽn da mi poorẽ, ad Wẽnd yaa Mitɑ n yaa Tõoda."
  16,71,"Lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩsɑ yãmb tɑɑb rɩtlẽ wã, lɑ b sẽn yɩɩs-b rãmbã pɑ yɩ n sak n kõ b rɩtlã b yembsã tɩ b fãɑ lebg ɑ yembr ye. Wẽnd neema wã la y mɑɑn sõm-zɩɩlem ne?"
  16,72,"La Wẽnd mɑɑnɑ pɑgb sẽn yi yãmb mensẽ wã n kõ yãmbɑ, la A leb n maan n kõ-ya sẽn yi yãmb pagbẽ wã kom-ribli la yagense, la A rɩlg yãmb rɩ-yɩlmã. Zĩri wã la b kõt sɩd ne-ɑ lɑ b yaool n mɑɑn sõm-zɩɩlem ne Wẽnd neemɑ wã?"
  16,73,"La b tũud zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, bũmb sẽn pa tar rɩtl n nɑ n kõ-b saasẽ bɩ tẽngã zugu; b pʋs n pɑ tõe."
  16,74,"Bɩ y ra mɑɑn wẽnes-n-taas ne Wẽnd ye, ad Wẽnd miime lɑ yãmb pa mi ye."
  16,75,"Wẽnd rɩka bilgri, yamb b sẽn so-a t'ɑ pɑ tar tõoga, ne Tõnd sẽn kõ ɑ soɑb rɩtl sẽn be neere, t'a yãkd-ɑ n nafdẽ sẽn solg la sẽn vẽneg pʋgẽ. Rẽ yĩngã nin-bãmbã b yiibã zema taaba? Pẽgr be ne Wẽnde! La ad b wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  16,76,"La Wẽnd leb n rɩka makr ne neb a yiibu, a yembrã yaa muka, a pa tõe n maan baa fʋɩ ye, n yaa zɩɩb a zu-soabã zugu; a zu-soabã sẽn tees-a zĩig ning fãa, a pa wat ne bõn-sõng ye, rẽ yĩnga yẽ soabã zema ned ning sẽn sagenda ne tẽeg-tɩrg la a leb n be so-tɩrg zugu?"
  16,77,"Ad sẽn solg saasẽ la tẽngẽ yaa Wẽnd n so, ad dũni wã yikr yell pa yɩ rẽndame t'a yaa wa nif-kamsg maa yẽ pẽnegrã n yɩɩde, ad Wẽnd yaa bũmbã fãa tõogda."
  16,78,"Ad yaa Wẽnd n yiis yãmb y ma-rãmbã pʋsẽ tɩ y pa mi baa fʋɩ, la A naan ninã la tʋbã la sũyã n kõ yãmba, tɩ sãnd-sãnde y na pʋʋs barka."
  16,79,"Rẽ yĩnga yãmb pa get luiili wã tɩ yɑɑ sẽn nom tɩ b be sɑɑsã ween-n-vɩʋʋgẽ, tɩ bũmb pa gãd-ba, rẽnda Wẽnd bala, ad bee woto pʋga sẽn yɑɑ tagmas-rãmb ne neb nins sẽn kõt sɩdã."
  16,80,"Lɑ Wẽnd maanɑ yãmb zɑgsã tɩ yaa yĩ-yõgneg zĩig n kõ yãmba, la A maan n kõ yãmb rũmsã gãnd tɩ y mɑɑn roto, t'ɑ yaa faag ne yãmb y yikr rɑɑre maa y tilgr rɑɑre, lɑ sẽn leb n yi rũmsã kõbdẽ, la yʋgma wã kõbdẽ lɑ rũm-bãɑnegã kõbdẽ tɩ yɑɑ rot-teed n le yɑɑ wʋm-noog n tɩ tãag wakat sẽn yãk toɑɑgɑ."
  16,81,"Lɑ Wẽnd mɑɑnɑme n kõ yãmb A sẽn naanã pʋgẽ mɑɑsem-dãmbɑ, lɑ A kõ yãmb tãensã pʋsẽ kõom zĩisẽ la A leb n kõ yãmb futu tɩ kogend yãmb n yi wĩndgã la gãnse tɩ kogend yãmb y zɑbrẽ. Yaa woto la A pidsd A neema yãmb zugu, tɩ sãnd-sãnde y na sak n tũ."
  16,82,"La b sã n gũd b zãn-kuidsã rẽnd ka rog fo zugu, rẽnda taasg sẽn yɑɑ vẽeneg bala."
  16,83,"B mii Wẽnd neemã wã, la b mɑɑnd sõm-zɩɩlem. Lɑ bãmbã wʋsg yaa kɩfr-dãmbã."
  16,84,"(Tẽeg) raar ning D sẽn na n tũus zãma pʋg fãa kaset soɑbɑ, rẽ poorẽ, b pa na n kõ kɩfr-dãmbã padeng ye, b pa na n leb n kõ-b sor tɩ b leb ye."
  16,85,"La wẽgdbã sã n wa yẽnd sɩbgrã, b pa na n yols b yĩngɑ, b pa na n koll-b me ye."
  16,86,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn maan lagem-n-taarã sã n wa yã b lagem-n-taasã, b yetame: ""d Soaba ad yaa bãmbã la tõnd lagem-n-taas nins d sẽn da yɩ n tũudẽ zẽng sẽn pa Foomã"". tɩ b lagem-n-taasã na n leok-bɑ n yeele: ""ad yãmb yaa zĩri-be-nebɑ."
  16,87,"Tɩ b na n sɑk n tũ Wẽnd ra-kãng raarã, tɩ bãmb sẽn da pasd zĩrĩ wã menem n bas bãmba."
  16,88,"Neb nins sẽn kɩfl la b gɩd (nebã) n yit Wẽnd sorã, D na n paas-b-la nang b nangã zugu, b sẽn da yɩ n sãamdẽ wã yĩngɑ."
  16,89,"(Tẽeg) raar ning Tõnd sẽn na n wa tʋms zãmã fãa pʋgẽ kaset soab sẽn yi b sʋka, lɑ D wa ne foom tɩ f na n yɩ kaset soɑb ne bãmbã rãmbã. Lɑ ɑd Tõnd sikɑ Alkʋrãanã n kõ foom tɩ yaa vẽnegr ne bũmbã fãa, n leb n yaa kãndagr la yolsg la sũ-noogr n kõ sɑk-n-tũ-rãmbã."
  16,90,"Ad Wẽnd sagenda ne tẽeg-tɩrg la manegre, la rog-pẽts sõngre, la A gɩdgd tʋʋm yood la yel-kiti la wẽgbo, A sagenda yãmb tɩ sãnd-sãnde y na tags n gese."
  16,91,"Lɑ pids-y Wẽnd pʋlengã tɩ y sã n rɩk-a, la y ra yidg pʋlengã a kengr poorẽ ye, tɩ yãmb yɑool n mɑɑnɑ Wẽnd t'A yɑɑ yãmb pʋlengã sεɛtɑ, ad Wẽnd mii yãmb sẽn maandã."
  16,92,"La y ra wa yɩ wa pag ning sẽn yidg a pãndã a sẽn nidg pãng n wĩ tɩ kẽ poorẽ, tɩ yãmb rɩkd y wẽenegã tɩ yaa zãmbg yãmb ne tɑɑb sʋkɑ, n rɑt tɩ yãmb zãma wã wil zãma zẽngã. Ad Wẽnd zarbda yãmb ne rẽnda, lɑ sẽn na yɩl n vẽneg n wĩnig-y yikrã raarã yãmb sẽn da yɩ n yõsd taab bũmb ning pʋgã."
  16,93,"Ad Wẽnd sã n da tʋllẽ, A rag n na maan yãmb tɩ y yaa zãma a yembre, la ad Wẽnd menesda A sẽn rata soab la A kãndagd A sẽn rat soaba, la ad b na n sok-y lame y sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  16,94,"Lɑ y rɑ wa rɩkd y wẽenegã tɩ yɑɑ zãmb yãmb ne taab sʋk ye, tɩ naoor rɑ wa salg a sẽn tabl poorẽ ye, tɩ y lemb nan-wẽngã yãmb sẽn da yɩ n gɩdgd Wẽnd sorã yĩngã. La be ne yãmba, nɑng sẽn zɩse."
  16,95,"Ra rik-y Wẽnd pʋlengã n tek ne ligd-bil ye, ad sẽn be Wẽnd nengẽ wã n yɩɩd sõmblem ne yãmba, tɩ y sã n dɑ miẽ."
  16,96,"Bũmb ning sẽn be yãmb nengẽ wã satame, la sẽn be Wẽnd nengẽ wã n paade, la ad Tõnd na n rola sug-maandbã b keoor neerem sẽn yɩɩd b sẽn da tʋmdã."
  16,97,"Ned ning sẽn tʋma sõma - yɑɑ rao tɩ yɑɑ pɑgɑ -, t'ɑ yaa sɩd-kɩta, D na vɩɩms a soab vɩɩm sẽn yɑɑ noogo, la D na rol-b keoor sõmblem sẽn yɩɩd b sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  16,98,"F sã n na n karem Alkʋrãanã, bɩ f kos gũudum ne Wẽnd n yi a Sʋtãan b sẽn rig n zãag ne yolsgã."
  16,99,"Ad a pa tar sor sɩd-kõtbã lɑ sẽn bobend b mensã ne b Soɑbã zug ye."
  16,100,"A pãngã yɑɑ neb nins sẽn lalld-ɑ wã lɑ a tõe, la sẽn maand-b lagem-n-taar ne Wẽndã."
  16,101,"Lɑ Tõnd sã n wa tedg Aayare, Aayar ɑ to zĩigẽ - lɑ Wẽnd n mi bũmb ning A sẽn sikdã - la b sẽn yete: ""tɩ fo yaa zĩri-be neda"". La pɑ woto ye, ad b wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  16,102,"Yeele: ""ad yaa yõ-yɩlengã (Malεk a Gibriil) n sig ne Alkʋrãanã, n yi fo Soabã nengẽ ne sɩda, sẽn na yɩl n tabl neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã, n leb n yaa kãndgr la sũ-noogr ne lɩslaambã."
  16,103,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd miime tɩ b yetame: "" yaa neb n wĩnigd-a (Alkʋrãanã)"" la zɩlemd ning b sẽn dõtã yaa bu-zẽnga, tɩ wãnde [Alkʋrãanã] yaa laarb-rãmb goam sẽn yaa vẽenega."
  16,104,"Ad neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne Wẽnd Aayayã, Wẽnd ka na n kãndg-b ye, la nang sẽn zabd be ne-ba."
  16,105,"Ad sẽn wãagd zĩri wã n rogendẽ wã yaa neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne Wẽnd Aayayã, bãmb me lɑ zĩri-be-nebã."
  16,106,"Ned ning sẽn kɩfla ne Wẽnd a sɩd-kũun loogr poorẽ, sã n pɑ ned ning b sẽn modg-ɑ t'a sũurã yaool n ket n tabend ne sɩd-kũuni, la sẽn yãɑg b yãoog ne kɩflmã gẽeg sẽn yi Wẽnd nengẽ be ne-ba, la nang sẽn zabd be ne-ba."
  16,107,"Woto, tɩ bala bãmb tũusa dũni vɩɩmã n nongẽ n yɩɩd yaoolem raarã, la Wẽnd pa kãndgad kɩfr-dãmb zãma ye."
  16,108,"Bãmb la neb nins Wẽnd sẽn pag b sũyã la b tʋbã la b ninã, bãmb me lɑ yam yaal-yaal rãmbã."
  16,109,"Sik ka be tɩ yaoolem raarã, bãmb la bõn rãmbã."
  16,110,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ, ad fo Soabã ne neb nins sẽn yik ne b dĩinã [Higrɑ] b sẽn nams-b poorẽ, rẽ poor tɩ b maan gihaadi la b maan sugri, ad fo Soabã rẽ loogr poorẽ, A yaa yaafg naaba n yaa yolsg naaba."
  16,111,"(Tẽeg) raar ning yõor fãa sẽn na n wa, n maan tak-n-taar n dat n fãag a mengɑ, tɩ B na n pids n dol yõor fãa bũmb ning a sẽn tʋmã, tɩ b pa na n wẽg bãmb ye."
  16,112,"Wẽnd gãnega bilgri, tẽng (Mɑkɑ) sẽn da tar bas-m-yam n yõgne, t'a rɩtlã wat-ɑ yol-yol n yit zĩig fãa, t'a maan sõm-zɩɩlem ne Wẽnd neema wã, tɩ Wẽnd na n leems-a kom lɑ pelen-yɩk b sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã yĩngɑ."
  16,113,"Lɑ Ad tẽn-tʋʋm n wa b nengẽ, sẽn yi bãmb pʋgẽ wã, tɩ b yags-a tɩ sɩbgrã rɩk-ba, tɩ b yɑɑ wẽgdbɑ."
  16,114,"Bɩ y rɩ bũmb ning Wẽnd sẽn pʋɩ n kõ yãmbã, tɩ yɑɑ halaal n yɑɑ yɩlenga, la y pʋʋs Wẽnd neema wã, tɩ y sã n yɩɩme n tũud Yẽ bɑlɑ."
  16,115,"Ad A sẽn harem ne yãmbã yaa gɩfo la zɩ-fudgdum la kurkuy nemdo, la b sẽn kodg n kõ lɑ b pʋd zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnd yʋʋre, la ned ning sẽn wɑ n pɑk ɑ soɑbɑ, tɩ pa kedgr n pa zʋʋg toɑɑga, rẽnd Wẽnd yaa yaafda n yaa yolsda."
  16,116,"Ra wa-y n yetẽ ne yãmb zεlmã wã sẽn sɩfd sẽn yaa zĩri wã: ""tɩ Wãnde yaa halaale tɩ wãnde yaa haraam"" n nɑ n wãagd zĩri n rogend Wẽnd ye. Ad neb nins sẽn wãagd zĩri n rogend Wẽndã pa na n tɩlg ye."
  16,117,"Yaa wʋm-noog bilf bɑlɑ, lɑ nan-zabdg be ne-bɑ."
  16,118,"Neb nins sẽn yaa Yahuud-rãmbã me, Tõnd harma b zug Tõnd sẽn karem n togs foom tɩ loogã, lɑ tõnd pɑ wẽg-b ye; ɑd b yɩɩme n wẽgd b mense."
  16,119,"Rẽ poorẽ, ad fo Soabã ne neb nins sẽn tʋm wẽngã ne zɩɩlemã, rẽ poorẽ tɩ b tuub la b maneg b tʋʋmã, ad fo Soabã rẽ poorẽ A yaa yaafg naab n yaa yolsg naaba."
  16,120,"Ad a ɭbraahɩɩm yɩɩ zãmɑ yẽ ɑ yembrã n duumd ne Wẽnd tũudum, n kɩlled n yit lɑgem-n-tɑɑre, a pa yɩ n nɑɑg lagem-n-taar rãmb lɑe."
  16,121,"N yaa bark pʋʋsd ne A neemã wã, ɑ Soɑbã tũus-ɑ lame la A kãndag-a n tʋg so-tɩrga."
  16,122,"La Tond kõ-a-la dũni kaanẽ pʋɩɩr sẽn be neere, la yaoolem raarã a bee nin-sõmã wã pʋgẽ."
  16,123,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Tõnd tʋms tɩ wɑ fo nengẽ: "" tɩ f tũ a ɭbraahɩɩm vũunã sẽn yaa sor sẽn kɩlled n yi lɑgem-n-tɑɑrã, a pa yɩ n naag lagem-n-taarã rãmb ye."
  16,124,"Ad b maana sibrã zɩsgr t'a yaa tɩlae ne neb nins sẽn yõs taab a pʋgẽ wã, la fo Soabã n na n bʋ n welg b sʋk yaoolem raarã, b sẽn da yɩ n yõsd taab bũmb ning zugã."
  16,125,"Bool n tʋg fo Soabã sorã ne yam la sagl-sõngo, la maan-b tak-n-taar sẽn yaa sõma n yɩɩdɑ, ad fo Soabã n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn menema n yi A sorẽ wã, Yẽ n leb n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn kãnda."
  16,126,"Lɑ y sã n na n sɩbge n dole, bɩ y sɩbg [bε wã] wala b sẽn sɩbg yãmb to-to wã, la y sã n maan sugri ad rẽnd n yɩɩd sõma ne sug-maandbã."
  16,127,"La maan sugri, lɑ fo sugrã pɑ yɩ rẽndɑ ne Wẽnd sεgl-sõngo, la f ra sãɑm f sũur b yĩng ye, la f ra pɑk f meng ne b sẽn maan rabã wã ye."
  16,128,"Ad Wẽnd bee ne neb nins sẽn zoet-A wã la neb nins sẽn yaa manegdbã."
